  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>For guests booked onto bed and breakfast or half board, meals can be enjoyed at the <strong>Casa Velha Restaurant. </strong>Each morning guests will have a breakfast buffet with cooked and continental options available from 7.30am to 10.30am. In the evening for guests booked onto half board, there is a set menu available with multiple options for each course. Dinner service takes place from 7pm to 9.30pm. </p>
<p><strong>Vista Balancal Restaurant</strong> offers a modern Portuguese menu infused with Mediterranean and traditional Madeiran cuisine, and showcases seasonal ingredients. Guests can enjoy both lunch and dinner here on the a la carte menu (booked and paid locally, hotel are able to provide a €25 credit per person for guests that wish to dine here for dinner instead of Casa Velha). </p>
<p><strong>Casa De Cha - Tea</strong> <strong>House</strong> is located next door within the Palheiro Gardens, meaning you can enjoy a delicious afternoon tea including sandwiches, salads, homemade cakes and more with a cup of tea or coffee, whilst taking in the fantastic garden views (booked and paid locally). </p>]]></cateringDescription>
