  <description><![CDATA[<p>Built in the 19th century Casa Velha do Palheiro is a beautiful hotel offering great quality and hospitality from the Blandy family.</p>
<h2>Fantastic facilities </h2>
<p>There are plenty of facilities at the Casa Velha do Palheiro. If you're looking for activities the hotel have badminton, tennis courts, table tennis and borders the Palheiro Golf Course with exclusive tee offs close to the hotel. Or, if you're looking for something to enjoy after a day exploring Funchal, make use of both the indoor and outdoor pools, or check out the spa facilities. </p>
<h2>Delicious dining </h2>
<p>Guests booked onto bed and breakfast and half board will have their meals at the Casa Velha Restaurant. The hotel also offer two more fantastic dining options (for a local charge), the Vista Balancal Restaurant is a great choice for either lunch or dinner (or both!). Here you'll find a fantastic menu offering a mix of Portuguese, Mediterranean and traditional Madeiran dishes. Or, head to Casa de Cha Tea House, and enjoy a traditional Madeiran afternoon tea amongst the beautiful Palheiro Gardens - perfect for a special occasion or just to treat yourself.</p>]]></description>
