  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Double Garden Wing Rooms</strong> are located in the garden wing with views of the garden, adjacent to the main building.</p>
<p><strong>Double Main House Rooms</strong> enjoy a period setting within the old house, these rooms are bright and airy. </p>
<p><strong>Double Garden Wing Rooms for sole use </strong>are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>En-suite bathrooms with showers </li>
<li>Air conditioning </li>
<li>Cable TV </li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Hairdryers </li>
<li>Daily turndown service </li>
</ul>
<p><strong>General information </strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Check in: 2pm</li>
<li>Check out: 12pm </li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Local fees and taxes</strong></p>
<p>A tourist tax of approx. €2.00 per person per night, for a maximum of 7 nights is payable locally for guests age 13 years and over (subject to change).</p>]]></roomsDescription>
